metadata.name: Bones
metadata.description:
She is the rude girl with a soft heart, the one with the dark and rebellious soul, with chaotic eyes who has gone down to her hell more than once in search of her smile and has returned intact, no matter if it is day or night, My demons are not hidden, they are the most attractive thing I have.

in collaboration with @serc1n
